query: WITH entities AS (SELECT collateralization_ratio, id FROM loans WHERE (collateralization_ratio > $3 OR (collateralization_ratio IS NOT DISTINCT FROM $3) AND COALESCE(id > $2, true)) ORDER BY collateralization_ratio NULLS FIRST, id LIMIT $1) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: LoanId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN loan_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.collateralization_ratio nulls first, i.id, i.id, e.sequence
